Content:: Edoardo Affini (born 24 June 1996 in Mantua) is an Italian cyclist, who currently rides for UCI WorldTeam Team Jumbo–Visma.[3][4] In October 2020, he was named in the startlist for the 2020 Giro d'Italia.[5] This biographical article related to an Italian cycling person born in the 1990s is a stub.
